<br />\n一句講晒 繼續做<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nBtw for 想體力升級/心態提升為民請命手足參考<br />\n補師我要幫全世界身心升level<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n順便入黎補補正能量整理下個人狀態<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n個人夠正能量先頂到落去<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n兄弟爬山 各做所長<br />\n若要勝利 必須備戰<br />\n營養＋運動 身心感覺同樣重要<br />\n<br />\n極權將破 在支爆前會係最黑暗嘅時候<br />\n我地要活得比以前好<br />\n堅持同改變<br />\n為香港付出多一點<br />\n<br />\n光復香港 時代革命<br />\n<br />\n和理勇武強身強心飲食入門：<br />\n全世界維持健康打落去<br />\n我出黎同時做幫大家上Buff<br />\n <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n人人都要有自衞隊身體質素<br />\n香港人 團結反抗<br />\n未來嘅希望由我地做起<br />\n<br />\nStep 8.心理健康❤️<br />\n當我地遇到情況📍 在安全情況下<br />\n⚡️減少重複接觸影響自己的負面人事<br />\n🍎做自己鍾意的事<br />\n😀約定 定期運動放鬆 <br />\n🧠睇書/聽Motivation Video<br />\n🔥最緊要痴住正能量嘅朋友/人（我😎）<br />\n<br />\n利申：健康教練<br />\nHerbalife  健康教練<br />\n唔係重點 重點係大家強身健體<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">全民皆兵</span></span> <br />\n依家風頭火勢<br />\n不分化 不割蓆 團結 正能量<br />\n呢個世界唔係我地影響人<br />\n就係人地影響緊我地<br />\n由改變自己 再感染多一個人<br />\n<br />\n永續健康身心 長期抗爭致勝<br />\n有咩搵我幫手 免費教大家<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n香港需要你<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有需 要TG 唔問名 <br />\n唔會問聯絡資料<br />\n同你Case Study <br />\n教你點飲食點運動<br />\n20％運動 80％營養<br />\n學完再善用Budget 搞好自己體能<br />\n如果想做下運動放鬆<br />\n歡迎黎搵我做下運動 <br />\n有街頭健身<br />\n<br />\nMy TG<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/TreeHoIsGood\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FTreeHoIsGood&d=Z9XWEpuBYzNDjlwSEAyqK%2F8K46P7%2BXxs1F7ZCKkfkQw%3D&h=8fc40f0b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/TreeHoIsGood</a><br />\nChannel<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/treehoHealthAdvice\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FtreehoHealthAdvice&d=Z9XWEpuBYzNDjlwSEAyqK%2F8K46P7%2BXxs1F7ZCKkfkQw%3D&h=59717d03\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/treehoHealthAdvice</a><br />\n討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/THHATalk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FTHHATalk&d=Z9XWEpuBYzNDjlwSEAyqK%2F8K46P7%2BXxs1F7ZCKkfkQw%3D&h=4ef3d47e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/THHATalk</a><br />\n長期戰爭 齊上齊落<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n對抗白色恐怖 <br />\n唔駛驚冇工開 <br />\n想開工/彈性part time<br />\n可以黎搵我 我cover你<br />\n反共抗中 我地勢不兩立<br />\nWe Shall Never Surrender<br />\n<br />\nUnited, We can win the fight"},{"pid":"68d5d02b927341dbae72434620e3bace0f769111","tid":1698224,"uid":37666,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"b13543555af66f3840e6eca6d0bb21a42936e85e","tid":1698224,"uid":253016,"like":23,"dislike":1,"score":22,"citedBy":6,"replyTime":"2019-11-07T10:57:36.000Z","msg":"俄畜 支那豬 坡狗<br />\n世界三大邪惡勢力"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-07T11:31:17.000Z","msg":"應該係俄 支 北韓<br />\n極權3大仆街"},{"pid":"cdac63f7b1eb1924145b54b9bc13e6b7e142a7f5","tid":1698224,"uid":73849,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-07T11:32:19.000Z","msg":"極權梗係驚人搞革命啦"},{"pid":"d14dbbce610bdf5d59a8e5ecf963285a0d84ee51","tid":1698224,"uid":105693,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-07T11:32:24.000Z","msg":"對任何政府黎講<br />\n平民最好日日努力工作，交足稅，而且唔好示威<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"84fd273e8fea0c9baf1794717cf913236da4576c","tid":1698224,"uid":78349,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"b13543555af66f3840e6eca6d0bb21a42936e85e","tid":1698224,"uid":253016,"like":23,"dislike":1,"score":22,"citedBy":6,"replyTime":"2019-11-07T10:57:36.000Z","msg":"俄畜 支那豬 坡狗<br />\n世界三大邪惡勢力"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-07T11:35:31.000Z","msg":"你漏左金仔同中東佬"},{"pid":"3eff35d96d7